==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nourishment
<hw>Nour"ish*ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>norrissement</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of nourishing, or the state of being
nourished; nutrition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which serves to nourish; nutriment;
food.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Learn to seek the <qex>nourishment</qex> of their souls.</q>
<rj><qau>Hooker.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nouriture</ent>⟦br⟧
